---
description: Frontend standards (Expo Router, NativeWind, components)
globs:
  - app/**
  - components/**
alwaysApply: false
---

- Routing
  - Use Expo Router file-based routing under `app/`
- Styling
  - Use NativeWind (Tailwind) for styling in React Native components
- Components
  - Prefer typed props, early returns, and shallow composition
  - Keep shared UI in `components/`
- Running the app
  - `bun run start` (or `bun run ios` / `bun run android` / `bun run web`)
